<a name="hotspotmining" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><ul class="hotspotminingNavbar clearfix">
<li class="active" data-id="426477">人物生平</li>
<li  data-id="389877">文学作品</li>
<li  data-id="387620">TA说</li>
</ul>
<div id="hotspotminingContent-426477" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=5929452dc7177f3e1061af4d16f208f1/4a36acaf2edda3ccf4386fbb0fe93901203f9249.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">唐代第一大牛人韩愈：一介书生独闯敌营，为万民以命相搏</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-06-10 11:06</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>世人常言三不朽，太上立德，其次立功，最下立言。韩愈正师道弘儒学，为百代之师，可谓功德无量；韩愈自动请缨，一介书生，独闯敌营，评定叛乱，可谓立功；韩愈文章千古，至情至性，可谓立言。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_rel_tit">相关新闻</div>
<ul class="hotspotminingContent_rel_cnt">
</ul>
