<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7aefb4f40b575a77f3dc7546&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=1a8f48b90ce939015657de7e1dd167d1/54fbb2fb43166d22291ce50d4b2309f79152d2c4.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7aefb4f40b575a77f3dc7546&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">韩愈位居“唐宋八大家”之首实至名归，他的这首劝诫诗写得真好</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2018-12-28 14:12</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>韩愈是唐朝著名文学家，很多人都熟悉他的《师说》，他被后人尊称为“唐宋八大家之首”不是没有原因的，他关于教学的很多思想，历经千百年，依然值得我们学习。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7aefb4f40b575a77f3dc7546&lemmaId=127407&lemmaId=127407&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
