<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="9167c87c318cf4c2f5d1c1ab">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=9167c87c318cf4c2f5d1c1ab&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/4610b912c8fcc3ce60e1e5649c45d688d43f2047.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
韩愈为唐宋八大家之首，但他戴镣铐跳舞式的写作，内心有多苦？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=9167c87c318cf4c2f5d1c1ab&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
这就是为什么本来很小众的古文，最后会得到了越来越多人的支持和反应，最后形成集体性的斗争浪潮，压倒了骈文，成为一场影响到宋代的文学运动。所以韩愈功不可没，被后人尊为“唐宋八大家”之首，并和同代的柳宗元、宋代的欧阳修、苏轼合称“四大天王”。没有韩愈，就没有这场唐代的“文艺复兴”。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-23</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">675</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="aaf4a9d8b6fb017f8386158d">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0fe67ca0&authorId=f97c8e26447fa302f5c2c220&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/64380cd7912397ddffbeacc15582b2b7d1a2872b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史客栈</strong>
<span>有趣味、有思维、有品位的“三味”历史</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=aaf4a9d8b6fb017f8386158d&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/95eef01f3a292df568dd9d8cb7315c6034a87308.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
比“卖炭翁”更有价值的“卖柴翁”，皇帝不允许这个故事流传
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=aaf4a9d8b6fb017f8386158d&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
应该说，这个故事无论从哪方面来看，都比卖炭翁的故事更有看点，也更有价值。然而，一千多年来，人们对卖炭翁耳熟能详，对卖柴翁却知之甚少，什么原因呢？</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-12-01</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">524</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="7a442b4090fe0fc8e0b3fb19">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=c2b37607&authorId=0c49bf38f5d8401ceb204423&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6a600c338744ebf82eac582dd7f9d72a6159a7c6.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>每天读文史</strong>
<span>文史专栏作者，资深诗词发烧友</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4090fe0fc8e0b3fb19&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/f9198618367adab44492dc2c85d4b31c8701e41b.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
韩愈写春天的一首名篇，蕴含人生哲理，读完受益良多，耐人寻味
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4090fe0fc8e0b3fb19&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
天地间绽放着尊贵的生命，也绽放着平凡的生命。比如伟人和芸芸众生，比如牡丹和苔花、杨花、榆荚。但是，每一个生命都有自己的风采，无论顺境还是逆境，都要用一颗坚强的心，把自己最美的一面，毫无保留地绽放给这个世界。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-04-20</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">360</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/91ef76c6a7efce1b293c3653a151f3deb48f6510.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
唐代第一大牛人韩愈：一介书生独闯敌营，为万民以命相搏
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=679728105ed9b11d5963cbc2&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
世人常言三不朽，太上立德，其次立功，最下立言。韩愈正师道弘儒学，为百代之师，可谓功德无量；韩愈自动请缨，一介书生，独闯敌营，评定叛乱，可谓立功；韩愈文章千古，至情至性，可谓立言。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-06-09</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">299</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0fe67ca0&authorId=f97c8e26447fa302f5c2c220&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/64380cd7912397ddffbeacc15582b2b7d1a2872b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史客栈</strong>
<span>有趣味、有思维、有品位的“三味”历史</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/472309f7905298221b23c755ddca7bcb0a46d410.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
真实的贾岛撞车事件，远比你知道的要残酷得多
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302&lemmaId=127407&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
贾岛的第一个故事版本能一直流传下来也就不难理解了，不光是文人在推崇，老百姓们也都很认可，因为它让人感受到了这个世界的温暖。至于故事的真和假，倒没那么重要了。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-07-14</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">221</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
